title: Sara Serna
text:
Sara Serna Abadías is a Spanish <a href="women%27s%20soccer">football</a> <a href="Striker%20%28association%20football%29">striker</a> currently playing in <a href="Segunda%20Divisi%C3%B3n%20%28women%29">Segunda División</a> for <a href="CE%20Seagull">CE Seagull</a>. She previously played for <a href="RCD%20Espanyol%20%28women%29">RCD Espanyol</a>, with whom she also played the <a href="2006-07%20UEFA%20Women%27s%20Cup">2006-07 European Cup</a>, <a href="UE%20L%27Estartit">UE L'Estartit</a> and <a href="FC%20Levante%20Las%20Planas">Levante Las Planas</a>.
She has been an <a href="Spain%20women%27s%20national%20football%20team">U-19 international</a>.
